room_title: Escape room "Dystopia" by Locked Adventures in San Marcos (CA)
room_address: 844 W. San Marcos, Blvd Suite 103, San Marcos, CA 92078
room_description: You live among survivors in a dystopian community. You and your group must split up to explore a nearby abandoned facility, gather as many supplies as you can, find the last twinkie on earth - that is rumored to be at this facility-and get out without getting bit, scratched or spit on.
